@startuml
actor User
participant AppLayout
participant BreakpointStore
participant Router

User -> AppLayout : open app
AppLayout -> BreakpointStore : read viewport
BreakpointStore --> AppLayout : mobile / tablet / desktop
AppLayout -> Router : render route shell
User -> AppLayout : resize / navigate
AppLayout -> BreakpointStore : recalculate
AppLayout --> User : adaptive nav UI
@enduml
